#: GMS2-Robohelp%5CGameMaker_Language%5CGML_Reference%5CDrawing%5CParticles%5CParticles.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:123-3
msgid ""
"Even though these effects are limited in scope and customisation, they can "
"still be used to create some simple, great effects with very little effort. "
"For example by creating a small puff of grey smoke below a moving missile in "
"each step, a pretty convincing smoke trail is created, so even when you are "
"an expert in particles it pays to remember that these effects exists as they "
"can still save you some time."
msgstr ""

